detailedDescription.articleBody: Alchip is a fabless semiconductor company founded in 2003 and headquartered in Taipei, Taiwan. Alchip specializes in the design and manufacture of digital CMOS ASICs.

detailedDescription.articleBody: ATI Technologies Inc. was a semiconductor technology corporation based in Markham, Ontario, Canada, that specialized in the development of graphics processing units and chipsets.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Fujitsu Limited is a Japanese multinational information technology equipment and services company headquartered in Tokyo. In 2018, it was the world's fourth-largest IT services provider measured by global IT services revenue.

detailedDescription.articleBody: PNY Technologies, Inc., doing business as PNY, is an American manufacturer of flash memory cards, USB flash drives, solid state drives, memory upgrade modules, portable battery chargers, computer locks, cables, chargers, adapters, and consumer and professional graphics cards.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: पीएनवाई टेक्नोलॉजीज, इंक, पीएनवाई के रूप में व्यवसाय कर रहा है, फ्लैश मेमोरी कार्ड, यूएसबी फ्लैश ड्राइव, सॉलिड स्टेट ड्राइव, मेमोरी अपग्रेड मॉड्यूल, पोर्टेबल बैटरी चार्जर, कंप्यूटर लॉक, केबल, चार्जर, एडेप्टर और उपभोक्ता और पेशेवर ग्राफिक्स का एक अमेरिकी निर्माता है।

detailedDescription.articleBody: Leyou is a Hong Kong based global video game holding company focused on free-to-play console and PC gaming. Leyou has five subsidiaries: Digital Extremes, Splash Damage, Athlon Games, Kingmaker and Radiance Games.
